# LiNKsites Foundation

LiNKsites is the **website factory**: many SMB sites from reusable Next.js templates, backed by **Payload CMS** and optional Supabase. Central CMS + hostname routing + premium spin-off deployments per README.

## Layout

- `apps/cms/` — Payload CMS (Next.js + Payload)
- `apps/web-master/`, `apps/web-company/` — site templates
- `packages/` — shared types, UI blocks, config, utils
- `supabase/` — migrations and functions
- `sites_specs/` — authoritative specs
- `docs/` — primary documentation index

## Modes

- Shared platform (many hostnames, one runtime) vs premium dedicated frontends—preserve `siteId` and CMS contracts when changing routing.
